column13: Independent Power Producer sells power to Golden Valley Electric Association.
In addition to Anchorage, CEA serves eight communities.
In addition to Valdez, the CVEA service area includes 14 communities.
Independent Power Producer sells power to Chugach Electric Association.
In addition to Fairbanks, the GVEA service are includes 25 communities.
In addition to Homer, HEA serves 24 communities.
The KEA service area also includes: Port Lions, Chiniak, Womens Bay and Woody Island.
